asset.title: ELEMENT AUSTRALIA WELCOMES CHRISTIAN LOW
asset.description: Hailing from the sunny shores of North Island, New Zealand, Christian picked up a skateboard when he was a young badger, and never let it leave his side. Winning New Zealand’s first ever SOTY in 2010 only added fuel to his fire, and influenced him to hop the pond over to Australia, where there was no slowing down. We’re proud to have watched Christian’s fluent style, and limitless creativity, and different outlook on the board develop over the years; Welcome to the Family.
asset.author: Element
